<section class="section aerys-diff" id="differentiation" aria-labelledby="diff-title">
  <div class="container">

    <span class="sec-label">Why AERYS™ Is Different</span>
    <h2 id="diff-title" class="aerys-diff__headline">
      Stop waking up with<br>
      <span class="hi">skin rashes and black residue.</span>
    </h2>

    <div class="aerys-diff__inner">

      <div>
        <p class="aerys-diff__body">Most mouth tapes use industrial acrylic adhesive &mdash; the same class used in packaging tape. It holds until it doesn&rsquo;t. And when it comes off, it takes skin cells with it. It leaves black marks on your upper lip. It pulls facial hair. It causes contact dermatitis in people with normal skin.</p>
        <p class="aerys-diff__body">This is not a minor issue with a workaround. It is a fundamental material failure.</p>
        <p class="aerys-diff__body">AERYS™ uses a pharmaceutical-grade silicone adhesive matrix &mdash; the same classification used in clinical wound dressings. It creates a complete seal that holds through eight hours of sleep, then releases cleanly from skin and hair with zero residue and zero trauma.</p>
        <p class="aerys-diff__body" style="font-weight:700;color:var(--text)">The result: a tape you can actually use every night. Which is the only way it works.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="aerys-compare__table" role="table" aria-label="AERYS vs competitors">
          <div class="aerys-compare__thead" role="row">
            <span></span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__thead-others">THE OTHERS</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__thead-aerys">AERYS™</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-compare__row" role="row">
            <span class="aerys-compare__attr">Adhesive Type</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__bad"><span class="aerys-compare__x" aria-hidden="true">&#10007;</span>Industrial acrylic glue</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__good"><span class="aerys-compare__check" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>Pharma-grade silicone</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-compare__row" role="row">
            <span class="aerys-compare__attr">Residue on Removal</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__bad"><span class="aerys-compare__x" aria-hidden="true">&#10007;</span>Black residue on skin</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__good"><span class="aerys-compare__check" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>Zero residue. Clean lift.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-compare__row" role="row">
            <span class="aerys-compare__attr">Skin Rashes</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__bad"><span class="aerys-compare__x" aria-hidden="true">&#10007;</span>Common complaint (2.4&#9733; avg)</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__good"><span class="aerys-compare__check" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>Derm-tested &middot; 0% rash rate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-compare__row" role="row">
            <span class="aerys-compare__attr">Beard Compatibility</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__bad"><span class="aerys-compare__x" aria-hidden="true">&#10007;</span>Pulls and destroys facial hair</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__good"><span class="aerys-compare__check" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>Beard-friendly. Not beard-destroying.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="aerys-compare__row" role="row">
            <span class="aerys-compare__attr">Removal Pain</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__bad"><span class="aerys-compare__x" aria-hidden="true">&#10007;</span>Reported as painful</span>
            <span class="aerys-compare__good"><span class="aerys-compare__check" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span>Gentle peel &mdash; no sting</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Feature cards -->
    <div class="aerys-features__grid" style="margin-top:3.5rem">

      <article class="aerys-feat">
        <div class="aerys-feat__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-feat__title">Zero-Residue Technology&#8482;</h3>
        <p class="aerys-feat__desc">Our silicone micro-matrix releases cleanly from skin and hair on every removal. No adhesive transfer. No morning clean-up. No evidence it was ever there.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="aerys-feat">
        <div class="aerys-feat__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-feat__title">Beard-Friendly Formula</h3>
        <p class="aerys-feat__desc">The silicone matrix flexes around follicles rather than bonding to them. Engineered for facial hair &mdash; because half the people who need this product have it.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="aerys-feat">
        <div class="aerys-feat__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-feat__title">Skin-Safe Promise&#8482;</h3>
        <p class="aerys-feat__desc">Hypoallergenic. Latex-free. Fragrance-free. Independently tested on all skin types including eczema, rosacea, and reactive skin. Zero rash rate across 30-night trials.</p>
      </article>

    </div>

    <div class="aerys-features__pills">
      <span class="aerys-pill">HSA / FSA Eligible</span>
      <span class="aerys-pill">Skin-Safe Promise&#8482;</span>
      <span class="aerys-pill">Engineered in the USA</span>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

